        If you want to start investing in mutual funds, ET Money's online portal simplifies the entire process.

        Explore now

        • Complete online KYC

          Simply fill in your name, birth date, upload ID and address proof to get KYC done instantly on ET Money.

        • Select a fund of choice

          Choose the mutual fund you want to invest in and the lumpsum or SIP investment amount.

        • Enter investment details

          Enter the amount of investment, the duration of investment, and the frequency (only for SIP investments).

        • Start investing

          Enter your bank details. If you want to start an SIP, set up a bank mandate to enable auto-debit for SIP.

          Voila! You are now set to invest in mutual funds!
